<!--
    Sparkle appcast for Provenance.

    Served at: https://procestra.app/appcast-provenance.xml
    (Provenance's SUFeedURL in Info.plist points here. On launch the
    app GETs this file and compares each <sparkle:version> against the
    installed CFBundleVersion; a higher number triggers an update
    prompt.)

    To publish a new version (see RELEASE.md / UPDATES.md):
      1) ./make-app.sh && ./make-dmg.sh   (signed + notarized .dmg)
      2) .build/artifacts/sparkle/Sparkle/bin/sign_update build/Provenance-<v>.dmg
         → prints sparkle:edSignature="…" length="…"
      3) Upload the .dmg to R2; update the <item> below (version,
         shortVersionString, pubDate, enclosure url + edSignature +
         length); deploy this file.
-->
